OL,7,FThe family of a man who died after
OL,8,Fbeing attacked in the St Paul's area
OL,9,Fof Bristol have paid tribute to a
OL,10,F"kind-hearted" and "beloved" member
OL,11,Fof the community.
OL,13,FHubert Brown, 61, from Easton, died
OL,14,Fafter being stabbed in Grosvenor Road
OL,15,Fon Friday 29 September. The incident
OL,16,Fis being treated as a race-hate crime.
OL,18,FA 36-year-old woman has been charged
OL,19,Fwith his murder and appeared at
OL,20,FBristol Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,21,F2 October.
